{
  "texts": [
    "The dataset includes more challenging cases, such as thermal crossover, small object, and fast motion, allowing for a comprehensive evaluation of the tracker.",
    "This dataset also extends the number of attributes to 12.",
    "The detailed description of attributes can be found in the ESM.",
    "The metrics are the same as those of GTOT, except that t pr is normally set to 20.",
    "In 2019, the researchers expanded the RGBT210 dataset and proposed RGBT234 [3], which provides ground truths for each modality."
  ]
}